headline: Why Symbotic Rocketed Some 16% Higher Today
summary: Today, Amazon CEO Andy Jassy said that Amazon's workforce would shrink going forward due to AI and automation.  While Amazon isn't a Symbotic customer, its competitors Walmart and Target are.  It's likely investors believe Amazon's AI-forward message will be beneficial for Symbotic, too.
